metadata.description:
This NFT acts as your key to the Sakura Sunset by ZENFT claim.

Sakura Sunset is a drink created for holders of Bonsai and Forest Spirits in a collaboration between ZENFT Studio & beverage specialists Calexo comprised of five unique flavors: white tea, lemongrass, black pepper, cardamom, and sandalwood. There are also  five different collectable can designs of varying rarity.

We hope you enjoy!
metadata.name: Sakura Sunset: Key
